import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# Generate some data
x = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
y = [2, 4, 6, 8, 10]

# Create a linear plot
plt.plot(x, y)

# Add labels and title
plt.xlabel('X-axis')
plt.ylabel('Y-axis')
plt.title('Linear Plot')

# Display the plot
plt.show()
